{"tid":1040062,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你中左六合彩會唔會番工?","createTime":"2019-02-27T23:13:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T08:52:59.000Z","uid":59844,"like":1018,"dislike":246,"uniUserReply":132,"replies":[{"pid":"415c6748c0bde7704da215f02331df0961195ef1","tid":1040062,"uid":59844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T23:13:44.000Z","msg":"當你人工由而家做到退休有3~4皮一個月，當你宜家30歲，有成30年要做埋，咁假設你中左一個3千萬6合彩，咁你仲番唔番工?<br />\n<br />\n當平均一個月有35k,30年工作所得金錢係:<br />\n35x12x30=12,600,000,即1千2百60萬。<br />\n中左一個3千萬六合彩已經完全cover晒有突，可以隨意做自己想做既野。<br />\n<br />\n正評:繼續番工<br />\n負評:即刻Quit<br />\n<br />\n利申:無中，不過成日FF中左會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea252bdb700e072187f4e84048208e872856cdfe","tid":1040062,"uid":40470,"like":425,"dislike":3,"score":422,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T23:15:53.000Z","msg":"照返工<br />\n<br />\n返工日日攪事<br />\n<br />\n串老細日日屌柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e4a86aa583f83a33fb82d795dbe9f8c8024d79c","tid":1040062,"uid":24989,"like":437,"dislike":10,"score":427,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T23:20:13.000Z","msg":"會立即買一間屋近公司，可以就咁行返去<br />\n<br />\n咁返工就唔駛再遲到，亦可以比平時瞓妟啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08022f7bc2b01e2f743b79a64bb05537c419623c","tid":1040062,"uid":108756,"like":244,"dislike":8,"score":236,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T23:20:47.000Z","msg":"當打份風流工 但都會搏升搏搵更多既錢"},{"pid":"f8e8af1c17a3e6d67b37c1229070363d755a9960","tid":1040062,"uid":33336,"like":210,"dislike":6,"score":204,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T23:40:51.000Z","msg":"返工同同事吹下水<br />\n<br />\n無社交會唔開心"},{"pid":"42eefadb3b52db4ad9bbe2f45d1e5a16d6a754f8","tid":1040062,"uid":37631,"like":87,"dislike":3,"score":84,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T23:41:21.000Z","msg":"會 買架靚車返工舒服d 又可以車埋同事老細"},{"pid":"5303f525ac646298226eb672aefcf0e6ab2e0d22","tid":1040062,"uid":40272,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T23:42:43.000